TELEM:Aggregator.TELEM:name: NVL
TELEM:Aggregator.TELEM:description: NVL Fixed PMT Telemetry aggregator at DMU samples definition and transformation rules

TELC:sample.name: XTAL
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Crystal clock count. Used as a reference count in converting many of the counters presented in this telemetry space.

TELC:sample.name: DIE_CSTATE_BLOCK_REFCNT
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Reference count for block cause counters. Counts the number of 10us intervals during which DieCstate entry was blocked at least once by any reason. To calculate percent blocked by a specific reason, divide corresponding block reason counter by this counter value.

TELC:sample.name: DIE_CSTATE_PREVENT_REFCNT
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Reference count for prevent cause counters. Counts the number of times DieCstate entry was blocked at least once by any reason. To calculate percent blocked by a specific reason, divide corresponding prevent reason counter by this counter value.
